cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AR, cs.SE

The paper is about a simulation platform for data centers, which involves both computation and communication resources. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses network and server performance analysis, which suggests cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as the second likely category. The paper proposes a simulation infrastructure, which involves system design and control, indicating cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the third likely category. The paper also mentions energy efficiency, which could fall under cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) or cs.SE (Software Engineering) as the fourth and fifth likely categories, respectively.
